    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go and looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
